###                  USERS MODULE                       ###

### Créer user
POST http://localhost:3000/users/signup
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "nouveau@xyz.com",
    "password": "abc123",
    "nomComplet": "Haroune Belhachani",
    "omnivoxDA": "0981234",
    "omnivoxPasswordHash": "somehash",
    "calendrierId": 1
}

### Login 
POST http://localhost:3000/users/signin
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "nouveau@xyz.com",
    "password": "abc123"
}

### Login ADMIN (Change email if necessary)
POST http://localhost:3000/users/signin
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@xyz.com",
    "password": "abc123"
}

### Who Am I (Requires valid cookie session)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/whoami

### Logout
POST http://localhost:3000/users/signout

### GET ONE User BY ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1

### GET ALL Users (Requires Admin Guard)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/

### Update User par ID
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/1
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "email_updated@xyz.com",
    "nomComplet": "Updated Name"
}

### Delete User par ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/1

### GET MESSAGE (ONLY ALLOWED IF LOGGED IN)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/message


###             PROGRAMMABLE MODULE                     ###

### Créer un Événement
POST http://localhost:3000/programmable/evenement
content-type: application/json

{
    "nom": "Examen Final",
    "description": "Examen de fin de session",
    "dateDepart": "2026-05-15T09:00:00Z",
    "dureeJours": 1
}

### Créer une Activité
POST http://localhost:3000/programmable/activite
content-type: application/json

{
    "nom": "Révision de groupe",
    "description": "Étudier pour l'examen de programmation",
    "dateDepart": "2026-05-10T14:00:00Z",
    "dureeHeures": 3,
    "priorite": "URGENT"
}

### Obtenir tous les programmables (Evenements et Activites )
GET http://localhost:3000/programmable

### Obtenir un programmable spécifique par id
GET http://localhost:3000/programmable/1